          "Holdout Method (80/20)",
          "{Accuracy: 0.76 - Logistic Regression, Precision: 0.91 - Logistic Regression, Recall: 0.77 - DT, F1-Score: 0.82 - DT}",
          "Authors in study 2 try to predict attrition of a MOOC at the end the of the 3rd out of 8 modules of an introductory programming course. \n\nThe first study involves tracking the submission history while the second involves the creation of a supervised model to predict attrition. ",
