    {
      "id": "23905712-6466-4226-8af0-1b5845020aac",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "MOOCs in programming are carachterized by a high rate of attrition of students. The authors of the study use data from MOOCs (logs and code submissions) to predict student disengagement. For that purpose, the authors use multiple classic ML algorithms.",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
        "id": "23905712-6466-4226-8af0-1b5845020aac",
        "parent": {
